videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu tosses a swing pass to Scottie Phillips, who does the rest for the 38-yard Ole Miss touchdown.
videos.headline: Ole Miss' Ta'amu slings a short pass for a TD

videos.description: Kent State RB Kavious Price catches a lateral and tosses an 18-yard touchdown to Jo-El Shaw.
videos.headline: Kent State pulls out the bag of tricks for TD

videos.description: Mississippi's A.J. Brown catches a 42-yard pass over his shoulder to set up a Scottie Phillips 2-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Ole Miss' 42-yard completion leads to 2-yard TD

videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu lofts a deep pass to D.K.  Metcalf, who uses one hand for an incredible 41-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Mississippi's Metcalf only needs one hand on 41-yard TD
